        "text_eGXbBJ": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The FitAI program is designed to help footwear retailers deliver highly personalized, scan-based shoe recommendations to their consumers—both in-store and online—by leveraging the proprietary SmartLast® database and Aetrex’s FitAI technology. The program helps retailers improve fit confidence, reduce returns, and boost conversion rates.</p>",
