            "highlighted_text": "text",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "text_piXTpr": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>As the FitAI InStore program gains traction, retailers can unlock new features that enhance the customer experience further. Once a retailer collects 5,000 scan to in-store purchase matching data points, <strong>FitAI Online</strong> can be activated. The software system can now begin using machine learning to refine its fit predictions, leveraging real-world buying behavior to move beyond rules-based matching and deliver even more accurate, data-driven recommendations. At this stage, shoppers who had previously completed a scan in store can identify themselves on the retailer’s website to receive personalized fit recommendations for available shoes.</p>",
            "text_font": "body",
            "text_size": "subtext-md",
            "text_max_size": 32,
            "text_line_height": 1.2,
